des:
This is the alexa skill used for getting chatbot facts.
We can ask questions about chatbots like 
what are chatbots?
How many types of chatbots are there?
You can even ask about the different types of chatbots.
etc.
This Skill is invoked by the trigger word "open chatbot fact". After the fact skill is opened you can ask anything about chatbot
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
